Analyze the performance implications of indexing the sale_date column in the Sales table, considering the types of queries commonly executed against this column.
Query:

-- Query without indexing
EXPLAIN ANALYZE
SELECT *
FROM Sales
WHERE sale_date = '2024-01-01';

-- Query with indexing
CREATE INDEX idx_sale_date ON Sales (sale_date);

EXPLAIN ANALYZE
SELECT *
FROM Sales
WHERE sale_date = '2024-01-01';
